{"id":"guide/template-syntax","title":"Template syntax","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/template-syntax.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"template-syntax\" translation-result=\"on\">模板语法<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-syntax#template-syntax\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Template syntax<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-syntax#template-syntax\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在 Angular 中，<em>模板</em>就是一块 HTML。你可以在模板中通过一种特殊的语法来使用 Angular 的诸多特性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">In Angular, a <em>template</em> is a chunk of HTML.\nUse special syntax within a template to build on many of Angular's features.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" translation-result=\"on\">前提条件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-syntax#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Prerequisites<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-syntax#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在学习模板语法之前，你应该熟悉下列内容：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Before learning template syntax, you should be familiar with the following:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/architecture\">Angular 的概念</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/architecture\">Angular concepts</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>JavaScript</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>HTML</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>CSS</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!--todo: Do we still need the following section? It seems more relevant to those coming from AngularJS, which is now 7 versions ago. -->\n<!-- You may be familiar with the component/template duality from your experience with model-view-controller (MVC) or model-view-viewmodel (MVVM).\nIn Angular, the component plays the part of the controller/viewmodel, and the template represents the view. -->\n<p translation-result=\"on\">应用程序中的每个 Angular 模板都是一块 HTML，你可以将其包含在浏览器显示的页面中。Angular 中的 HTML 模板与常规 HTML 一样，可以在浏览器中渲染视图或用户界面，但功能要多得多。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Each Angular template in your application is a section of HTML to include as a part of the page that the browser displays.\nAn Angular HTML template renders a view, or user interface, in the browser, just like regular HTML, but with a lot more functionality.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用 Angular CLI 生成 Angular 应用时，<code>app.component.html</code> 文件是一个包含占位符 HTML 的默认模板。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">When you generate an Angular application with the Angular CLI, the <code>app.component.html</code> file is the default template containing placeholder HTML.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">本模板语法指南向你展示了如何通过协调类和模板之间的数据来控制 UX/UI。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The template syntax guides show you how to control the UX/UI by coordinating data between the class and the template.</p>\n\n<div class=\"is-helpful alert\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\">大多数模板语法指南都有专门的可工作的范例应用，这些应用程序演示了每个指南中的各个主题。要查看把所有应用合在一起时的工作情况，请参阅综合<live-example title=\"Template Syntax Live Code\"></live-example>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Most of the Template Syntax guides have dedicated working example applications that demonstrate the individual topic of each guide.\nTo see all of them working together in one application, see the comprehensive <live-example title=\"Template Syntax Live Code\"></live-example>.</p>\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"empower-your-html\" translation-result=\"on\">为你的 HTML 赋能<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-syntax#empower-your-html\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Empower your HTML<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-syntax#empower-your-html\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在模板中使用 Angular 的特有语法来扩展应用程序的 HTML 词汇表。比如，Angular 可以通过内置的模板函数、变量、事件监听和数据绑定等功能来帮助你动态获取和设置 DOM（文档对象模型）中的值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Extend the HTML vocabulary of your applications With special Angular syntax in your templates.\nFor example, Angular helps you get and set DOM (Document Object Model) values dynamically with features such as built-in template functions, variables, event listening, and data binding.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">几乎所有的 HTML 语法都是有效的模板语法。但是，由于 Angular 模板只是整个网页的一部分，而不是整个网页，因此你不需要包含诸如 <code>&lt;html&gt;</code>，<code>&lt;body&gt;</code> 或 <code>&lt;base&gt;</code> 元素。这样你可以专注于正在开发的那部分页面。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Almost all HTML syntax is valid template syntax.\nHowever, because an Angular template is part of an overall webpage, and not the entire page, you don't need to include elements such as <code>&lt;html&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;body&gt;</code>, or <code>&lt;base&gt;</code>, and can focus exclusively on the part of the page you are developing.</p>\n\n<div class=\"alert is-important\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\">为了消除脚本注入攻击的风险，Angular 不支持模板中使用 <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> 元素。Angular 会忽略 <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> 标记，并向浏览器控制台输出一条警告。欲知详情，参阅<a href=\"guide/security\">“安全性”</a>页面。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To eliminate the risk of script injection attacks, Angular does not support the <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> element in templates.\nAngular ignores the <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> tag and outputs a warning to the browser console.\nFor more information, see the <a href=\"guide/security\">Security</a> page.</p>\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"more-on-template-syntax\" translation-result=\"on\">关于模板语法的更多信息<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-syntax#more-on-template-syntax\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">More on template syntax<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-syntax#more-on-template-syntax\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">你可能还对下列内容感兴趣：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">You might also be interested in the following:</p>\n\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">主题</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Topics</nt-wrapper></th>\n<th align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">详情</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Details</nt-wrapper></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/interpolation\">插值</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/interpolation\">Interpolation</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">学习如何在 HTML 中使用插值和表达式。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to use interpolation and expressions in HTML.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/template-statements\">模板语句</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/template-statements\">Template statements</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">响应模板中的事件。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Respond to events in your templates.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/binding-syntax\">绑定语法</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/binding-syntax\">Binding syntax</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">使用绑定来协调应用程序中的值。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Use binding to coordinate values in your application.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/property-binding\">property 绑定</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/property-binding\">Property binding</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">设置目标元素的属性或指令中带 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</code> 装饰器的属性。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Set properties of target elements or directive <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</code> decorators.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/attribute-binding\">属性（Attribute），类和样式绑定</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/attribute-binding\">Attribute, class, and style bindings</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">设置 Attribute、类和样式的值。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Set the value of attributes, classes, and styles.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/event-binding\">事件绑定</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/event-binding\">Event binding</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">监听事件和 HTML。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Listen for events and your HTML.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/two-way-binding\">双向绑定</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/two-way-binding\">Two-way binding</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">在类及其模板之间共享数据。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Share data between a class and its template.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/built-in-directives\">内置指令</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/built-in-directives\">Built-in directives</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">监听和修改 HTML 的行为和布局。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Listen to and modify the behavior and layout of HTML.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/template-reference-variables\">模板引用变量</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/template-reference-variables\">Template reference variables</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">U 使用特殊变量来引用模板中的 DOM 元素。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Use special variables to reference a DOM element within a template.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/inputs-outputs\">输入和输出</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/inputs-outputs\">Inputs and Outputs</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">在父级上下文和子指令或组件之间共享数据</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Share data between the parent context and child directives or components</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/template-expression-operators\">模板表达式运算符</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/template-expression-operators\">Template expression operators</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">了解管道运算符 |，以及如何防范空值 <code>null</code> 或 <code>undefined</code>。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Learn about the pipe operator (<code>|</code>), and protect against <code>null</code> or <code>undefined</code> values in your HTML.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/svg-in-templates\">模板中的 SVG</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/svg-in-templates\">SVG in templates</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">动态生成交互式图形。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Dynamically generate interactive graphics.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间： 2/28/2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/architecture-components\n - guide/architecture-next-steps\n - guide/component-overview\n - guide/example-apps-list\n - guide/forms\n - guide/glossary\n - guide/understanding-angular-overview\n - guide/what-is-angular\n - start/start-deployment\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/Input\n - guide/architecture\n - guide/attribute-binding\n - guide/binding-syntax\n - guide/built-in-directives\n - guide/event-binding\n - guide/inputs-outputs\n - guide/interpolation\n - guide/property-binding\n - guide/security\n - guide/svg-in-templates\n - guide/template-expression-operators\n - guide/template-reference-variables\n - guide/template-statements\n - guide/template-syntax#empower-your-html\n - guide/template-syntax#more-on-template-syntax\n - guide/template-syntax#prerequisites\n - guide/template-syntax#template-syntax\n - guide/template-syntax#为你的-html-赋能\n - guide/template-syntax#关于模板语法的更多信息\n - guide/template-syntax#前提条件\n - guide/template-syntax#模板语法\n - guide/two-way-binding\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/template-syntax.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n-->"}